From: Wei Yang <Wei.Yang@windriver.com>
Date: Mon, 24 Sep 2012 11:11:27 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 04/21] fsl-p2020:Add DS1339 RTC device node for P2020DS

There are two RTC devices on fsl_p2020DS board, one(rtc_cmos)
is on ISA bus using i8259 interrupt controller, the other(ds1339)
is on I2C-1 bus.

Signed-off-by: Andrew Liu <shengping.liu@windriver.com>
Signed-off-by: Yongli He <yongli.he@windriver.com>
---
 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p2020ds.dtsi |    8 ++++++++
 1 file changed, 8 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p2020ds.dtsi b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p2020ds.dtsi
index 731f148..058e25e 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p2020ds.dtsi
+++ b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p2020ds.dtsi
@@ -145,6 +145,14 @@
 		};
 	};
 
+   i2c@3100 {
+
+	   rtc@68 {
+		       compatible = "dallas,ds1339";
+			   reg = <0x68>;
+	   };
+   };
+
 	usb@22000 {
 		phy_type = "ulpi";
 		dr_mode = "host";
